name: BlueBerry
description: Just like their close relative, the peach, nectarines are a truly delectable, juicy fruit. And with smooth, fuzz-free skins, nectarines are particularly wonderful in fruit salads, crisps, crumbles and cakes. Or simply enjoy eating them out of hand for sweet, sunshiny delight.
